data.description: Top floor, 3 bedroom/2bath condo in the highly sought out Foxcroft Condo Community.  Conveniently located in Sandy Springs, near parks, restaurants, shopping and schools. This warm and inviting space has everything you want and need while enjoying a simple lifestyle close to all things Sandy Springs!  Rich hardwoods throughout the living and dining room, carpet in bedrooms.  The huge owners suite boasts a large walk-in closet and en-suite with double vanity.  Additional bedrooms are well portioned and share a large bathroom.  Third bedroom/den has an inviting fireplace.  Great walkability too! This one is a must see! Foxcroft - the hidden gem of Sandy Springs! (Rental Restrictions and NO FHA)
